data.title: Medicare Supplements, Medicare Part D
data.meta_description: We can help you figure out the best Medicare Health insurance Plan options including Medicare Supplement, Medicare Advantage and Part D Prescription drug plans.
data.text:
Our Mission - Helping You with Medicare Insurance

To help you navigate the complexities of Medicare Advantage, Medicare Supplements and Medicare Part D. To share with you the pros and cons of various options and help you converge on the best solution for your situation.

To represent the companies we are contracted with in a transparent manner. To share with you the pros and cons of various options and help you decide and choose the best solution for you.

Insurance products can be complicated, confusing and frustrating. There are some unique words in the insurance vocabulary. We act as your interpreter to “insure” your complete understanding.

Our Process

First, we ask enough questions to help you choose the best Medicare insurance solution for you. In some cases, we have forms that we ask you to complete so you will receive the best recommendation. Second, we do research (if needed). Third, you’ll receive suggestions on the most suitable solution for you.

To more completely serve you we project ourselves into your situation and circumstances. Then, we ask ourselves “what would I do if I were this person?” Sometimes, there is a clear and unique solution. More often, there are several possibilities that require us to further discuss and clarify what’s most important to you. Our goal is to uncover the optimal solution for you.

Jerry has been a licensed insurance agent for 26 years. During his career, he has been involved primarily with health insurance in one form or another. He has traveled around the states speaking to other insurance agents on various health related products and services.

Currently he is focused on Medicare health plan options and has done so for a number of years. This is what he plans to do for the balance of his career.

Jerry says that working with seniors is a pleasure and looks forward to helping them with understanding the 'alphabet soup' of plans and benefits that are associated with Medicare. As confusing as this can be, by spending a bit of time with him, he can can make a difference in your Medicare health plan options choices. His ultimate goal, since everyone has different needs, likes and dislikes, he does not try to fit his clients to a specific plan, but will find a plan that fits them.
